Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:16.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好 感冒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:19.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:23.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你端了杯水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:24.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:30.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 姐姐
